Package: sup
Title: Propagate uncertainties in numerical computations
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Dan",
           family = "Kelley",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kelley.dan@gmal.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7808-5911"))
Description: This package creates `%+%` as a new binary operator that adds two items and also propagates the uncertainties of those items. Similar operations are performed with `%-%`, `%-%`, `%*%` and `%/%`.
